<body>
<div type="letter">
    <pb facs="3531546" n="1"/>
<opener>
    <lb/>Viro incomparabili Dan. Bernoullio Greg. Fontana sal. dic.
</opener>
    <p>
        <lb/>Anceps h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>reo, utrum epistola 40 ante diebus ad Te scripta
        <lb/>ad tuas manus pervenerit nec ne. In hac qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rebam a Te,
        <lb/>num tibi gratum futurum fuerit si epistola, quam a Te
        <lb/>pridem accepi, evulgaretur; simulque Tecum nonnulla de libro
        <lb/>meo jam edito communicabam. Nihil in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiarum aliud Te
        <lb/>rogo, quam ut mihi notum facias, utrum eandem accepiris.
        <lb/>Vale, Vir summe, saluta a me plurimum Tuos omnes, me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que ama.
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/>Dab. Ticini Regii, sen (<hi rend="u">en</hi> <hi rend="u">Pavie</hi>) Kal. Nov.
        <lb/>1771.
    </p> 
    <pb facs="3531547" n="2"/>
    <closer>
        <address>
            <addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Monsieur Daniel Bernoulli</addrLine>
            <addrLine>trés-celebre Mathematicien </addrLine>
            <addrLine>à</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Bale</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Suisse</addrLine>
        </address>
    </closer> 
</div>
